headline: IQVIA AI Assistant wins 2024 PM360 Innovation Award for Artificial Intelligence
summary: RESEARCH TRIANGLE PARK, N.C., February 24, 2025--IQVIA (NYSE:IQV), a leading global provider of advanced analytics, technology solutions and clinical research services to the life sciences and healthcare industries, today announced that IQVIA AI Assistant has been awarded a 2024 PM360 Innovation Award in the Artificial Intelligence category.
